<body>

<p>If you would like to delete your Vibe Reader account and all associated personal data, please follow the steps below.</p>

<hr>

<h2>How to delete your account</h2>

<h3>Option 1: In the app</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Open the <strong>Vibe Reader</strong> app.</li>
  <li>Go to <strong>Settings → Account → Delete Account</strong>.</li>
  <li>Confirm your request when prompted.</li>
</ol>

<p>Your account and data will be scheduled for deletion immediately.</p>

<hr>

<h2>What data will be deleted</h2>

<p>When you delete your account, the following data will be <strong>permanently removed</strong> from our systems:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Email address and profile information</li>
  <li>Saved articles, highlights, and reading history</li>
  <li>AI-generated summaries and preferences</li>
  <li>Subscription status and plan details</li>
</ul>

<hr>

<h2>Data we may retain temporarily</h2>

<p>For legal, security, or billing compliance purposes, certain data may be retained for a limited period after account deletion:</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Data type</th>
      <th>Retention period</th>
      <th>Reason</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>Payment and transaction records</td>
      <td>Up to 180 days</td>
      <td>Tax and accounting obligations</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>Fraud and abuse prevention logs</td>
      <td>Up to 90 days</td>
      <td>Security and legal compliance</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>After the retention period expires, this data will be securely deleted.</p>

<hr>

<h2>Questions?</h2>

<p>If you have any questions about account deletion or your personal data, please contact us at <a href="mailto:vibe-reader-support@seekrtech.com">vibe-reader-support@seekrtech.com</a></p>

</body>
</html>
